** '''Grim Reaper:''' just revenge on those who didn't save his mother. Revenge on every living person, for in his mind, no-one deserved to live if his mother couldn't.
** '''Grim Reaper:''' Jonas went to the island, and killed them all. Almost every living soul on that island met their grisly end thanks to that boy. 65 dead. The entire island, save for one man.
** '''Player:''' And that one man was Jarvis?
